column4: 'title': [u'\n                    Chicco Baby Moments No Tears Shapmoo 200 ml            ']
column14:
'desc': [u'

Chicco Baby Moments No Tears Shapmoo 200 ml (200 ml) Price: Rs.189

Giving the first bath to your baby can always raise concerns in your mind. The gentleness and safety of the products that are used on the baby’s skin has to be made sure before they are used. The Chicco No Tears Gentle Shampoo is a soft shampoo that can be used to cleanse your little one’s skin. This Chicco Shampoo uses a\xa0no tears formula that ensures you that your baby’s delicate eyes will not be irritated by this Chicco Gentle Shampoo.

After using the Gentle Shampoo on the baby’s scalp her hair will become more manageable and tangle free. SLS or Sodium Laureth Sulfate and soap is not present in this Gentle Shampoo from Chicco which makes it absolutely suitable for your bundle of joy’s delicate skin. This microbiologically and dermatologically tested Chicco Gentle Shampoo is easy to lather and rinse off. It will leave your angel’s scalp and hair clean and healthy.

column4: 'title': [u'\n                    Chicco Spin n Squirt Duckling Bath Toy            ']
column14:
'desc': [u'

Chicco Spin n Squirt Duckling Bath Toy Price: Rs.599

Very few kids like having a bath and when you force them to take one
column15:
they get fussy. Make bath time fun by adding bath toys that float in the water for your kids to play with. The Chicco Spin n Squirt Duckling Bath Toy is the first bath toy you should pick up as the rubber duckling is the most popular. This duckling can spin around without toppling and can also squirt water when pressed. This bath toy is perfect for both boys and girls in the age group of 6 to 24 months who love birds. Spray water for added fun by pressing the button on the back.
